{"tid":739081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普通求婚已過時 法國婚禮公司推「登月求婚」Plan ，一次11億港紙","createTime":"2018-07-12T00:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T13:51:25.000Z","uid":66943,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5b94e8add0d4d03e9dabcbf6eb4e165655e7b8de","tid":739081,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:24:20.000Z","msg":"正當我們絞盡腦汁想求婚方法的時候，殊不知已經帶著自己的愛人飛向月球進行求婚了！也將那句&ldquo;如果摘下月亮我就嫁給你&rdquo;的無稽之談變為可能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/081534_7f0c4e58f1c4d582489bf90d828ef46c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F081534_7f0c4e58f1c4d582489bf90d828ef46c.jpg&h=ad45d02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，&ldquo;月球求婚&rdquo;計劃是由法國巴黎一家婚禮策劃公司ApoteoSurprise所籌劃，其創辦人Nicholas Garreau是一名航空工程師，該公司表示其最終目標，是要做出&ldquo;13.8億年來最瘋狂、最非凡的求婚驚喜&rdquo;。在求婚當天，戀人雙方將從佛羅里達州卡納維爾角的Kennedy Space Center起飛，在首度進入無重狀態時，會播放Strauss的《Thus spoke Zarathustra, Op.30》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/081547_1bfdd8f8b8133b1436056c0b539d4138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F081547_1bfdd8f8b8133b1436056c0b539d4138.jpg&h=d4b42f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依照時間表，在三天後，情侶將順利抵達月球軌道，並在200-300公里的高空與行星飛行，在飛行到軌道中段的時候，將會在飛船裡播放Frank Sinatra的《Fly Me to the Moon》，這時候準新郎將會從西裝外套裡拿出準備好的戒指，在渺無人煙的太空中向心上人求婚。而這趟浪漫的求婚之旅，將在兩人欣賞完月球隕石坑背後的壯觀日出後進入尾聲，最後飛回大氣層著陸，結束將近一周的旅程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/081600_09de89bf065fa8a4648ad7c26e5f4135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F081600_09de89bf065fa8a4648ad7c26e5f4135.jpg&h=ebf44326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這一計劃會在2020年3月後開放網上預約，報名五個月後，雙方都必須接受體能訓練和12週的技術訓練。整個行程費用為1.45億美元（約11億港元）。"},{"pid":"1bafeae51b7b4d5d23e25a90d47fca9cfffb669b","tid":739081,"uid":42084,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:37:27.000Z","msg":"雙方都必須接受體能訓練和12週的技術訓練<br />\n<br />\n女方都要訓練黎被求婚 咁呢個仲係求婚咩"},{"pid":"e49473fc5096c9881c11509d6172a2681508dfd4","tid":739081,"uid":51720,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:39:39.000Z","msg":"噱頭意義大於實際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf1a83763353d9d8aa1811a0e4d5f1bc4e98dcb","tid":739081,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:41:37.000Z","msg":"女方體能承唔承受得起6G既壓力？<br />\n可能淨係得蜘蛛女呢d體能怪先應乎到"},{"pid":"6dab910a73e16e202640883cff73235fe6b27c65","tid":739081,"uid":108347,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"quote":{"pid":"1bafeae51b7b4d5d23e25a90d47fca9cfffb669b","tid":739081,"uid":42084,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:37:27.000Z","msg":"雙方都必須接受體能訓練和12週的技術訓練<br />\n<br />\n女方都要訓練黎被求婚 咁呢個仲係求婚咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"Honey呀，我呢就想同你求婚，不過呢就要一齊訓練3個月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你覺得條女會點答你?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定應承，因為你拎得出11億求婚一定好撚有錢，訓練3年都滯"},{"pid":"d704ae3d87c373a545f0b3125eacc645a0f625c0","tid":739081,"uid":89683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔播埋林子祥嘅分分鐘需要你？"},{"pid":"c78958ee20590edd5b2d87c9dc838c3a874981e1","tid":739081,"uid":45368,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"6dab910a73e16e202640883cff73235fe6b27c65","tid":739081,"uid":108347,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"quote":{"pid":"1bafeae51b7b4d5d23e25a90d47fca9cfffb669b","tid":739081,"uid":42084,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:37:27.000Z","msg":"雙方都必須接受體能訓練和12週的技術訓練<br />\n<br />\n女方都要訓練黎被求婚 咁呢個仲係求婚咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"Honey呀，我呢就想同你求婚，不過呢就要一齊訓練3個月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你覺得條女會點答你?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />